data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3-bedroom townhome is ready for immediate occupancy and offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and exterior space. Step into a recently remodeled space, featuring an updated kitchen with maple cabinets, tiled floors, and stainless steel appliances. Remodeled baths that allow you to move in and start enjoying your new space.   Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry, making daily chores a breeze. The heart of this home is its spacious living room/dining room combo, providing an open and inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertaining. With freshly painted interiors, the townhome exudes a clean and fresh ambiance, creating the perfect canvas for your personal touch while enjoying large windows with natural light. The primary bedroom has 2 closets and sliders to a cozy balcony. The second bedroom is huge with a large walk-in closet.  Storage space in the garage as well as under the stairs. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this townhome offers not just a home but a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own and start the New Year as a homeowner! AC was replaced in 2015- and new garage opener 1 year ago. To see it is to love it!
